### Screen: Quick Workout Preview (NEW)

When user taps "Tập Ngay", an algorithm picks a random workout type and generates exercises to fill the chosen time (default 1h).

**Top section:**
- Workout name displayed prominently (e.g., "🔥 Chest Day", "💪 Upper Body", "🦵 Leg Day")
- Auto-suggested by algorithm (random rotation)

**Control buttons (grid/list):**

1. **🔄 Thay đổi bài tập** — Opens a new sub-screen with:
   - Muscle group buttons: Chest Day, Back Day, Leg Day, Cardio Day, Upper Body Day, Push Day, Pull Day, Lower Body Day
   - My Saved Workouts — loads from localStorage (same as existing profiles)
   - Create New Workout — goes to existing Workout Setup screen

2. **⏱️ Thời gian: 1h** — Tappable button to cycle duration (15min → 3h, step 15min). Regenerates exercises on change.

3. **🏢 Phòng tập** — Change gym (placeholder for now, shows "Coming soon")

4. **💪 Cường độ** — Intensity selector: Beginner, Intermediate, Hardcore, Cardio, De-load. Changes sets/reps/rest parameters.

5. **🧱 + Core Workout** — Toggle to add core exercises at the end

6. **🧘 + Warmup/Cool down** — Toggle to add warmup & cooldown

**Below controls: Exercise list preview** showing generated exercises with sets/reps/rest.

**Bottom: "Bắt đầu tập 🔥" button** to start the workout.

