### Workout Generation Algorithm

A new file `workout-generator.js` will contain:

**Workout types with exercise mapping:**
| Workout Type | Categories Used |
|---|---|
| Chest Day | Chest + Triceps |
| Back Day | Back + Biceps |
| Leg Day | Legs |
| Upper Body Day | Chest + Back + Shoulders |
| Push Day | Chest + Shoulders + Triceps |
| Pull Day | Back + Biceps |
| Lower Body Day | Legs |
| Cardio Day | Light compound movements |

**Time-based exercise selection:**
- Algorithm calculates time per exercise: `(sets × reps × SEC_PER_REP) + ((sets-1) × rest)`
- Picks exercises until total time ≈ target duration
- Adjusts sets/reps based on intensity level

**Intensity modifiers:**
| Intensity | Sets Modifier | Reps Modifier | Rest Modifier |
|---|---|---|---|
| Beginner | ×0.7 | ×0.8 | ×1.3 |
| Intermediate | ×1.0 | ×1.0 | ×1.0 |
| Hardcore | ×1.3 | ×1.2 | ×0.8 |
| Cardio | ×1.0 | ×1.5 | ×0.5 |
| De-load | ×0.6 | ×0.7 | ×1.5 |

**Core exercises (added when toggled):**
- Plank, Crunches, Russian Twist, Leg Raises, Mountain Climbers

**Warmup/Cooldown (added when toggled):**
- Warmup: Jumping Jacks, Arm Circles, Hip Circles, Light Cardio
- Cooldown: Static Stretches, Deep Breathing

